rom your team are representing their country at the 2026 World Cup in the United States, Canada and Mexico?","image":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0525/r1663354_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","premium":false,"published":"2026-06-17T06:51:08Z","logoSrc":"https://a.espncdn.com/redesign/assets/img/logos/espnplus/espnplus-2x.png","images":[{"src":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0525/r1663354_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","alt":"World Cup 2026: Which players from your Premier League team are going?"}],"link":"/soccer/story/_/id/48709856/world-cup-2026-which-players-your-premier-league-team-going"},{"id":48823863,"headline":"Meet England's 2026 World Cup squad: All 26 players picked by Thomas Tuchel and why","byLine":"ESPN","description":"ESPN takes a look at every player named in the England squad for the 2026 World Cup.","image":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0522/r1661870_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","premium":false,"published":"2026-06-17T06:50:12Z","logoSrc":"https://a.espncdn.com/redesign/assets/img/logos/espnplus/espnplus-2x.png","images":[{"src":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0522/r1661870_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","alt":"Meet England's 2026 World Cup squad: All 26 players picked by Thomas Tuchel and why"}],"link":"/soccer/story/_/id/48823863/meet-england-2026-world-cup-squad-26-players-picked-thomas-tuchel-why"},{"id":49090801,"headline":"Harry Souttar is defying all odds -- again -- to star at a World Cup","byLine":"Joey Lynch","description":"In Australia's win over Türkiye, Harry Souttar clocked one of the fastest sprints seen at the World Cup so far. It was an amazing feat given that the Socceroos centre back has barely played in four years.","image":"https://a.espncdn.com/combiner/i?img=/photo/2026/0617/r1674669_1296x729_16-9.jpg&w=220","premium":false,"published":"2026-06-17T06:47:00Z","logoSrc":"https://a.espncdn.com/redesign/assets/img/logos/espnplus/espnplus-2x.png","images":[{"src":"https://a.es